        <h3 class="heading-medium">Desired skills &amp; qualities</h3>
        <p>You need to have a keen interest in the health and fitness industry.</p>
        <p>You must be enthusiastic and able to work well in a team.</p>
        <h3 class="heading-medium">Other information</h3>
        <p>Consisting of a 12 week programme, the first week is totally guided learning with one of our tutors (Monday –Friday) weeks 2-7 will consist of the student attending the placement work place 3 days a week full time and an additional 2 days a week will be back in the classroom with the tutor, weeks 8-12 will the totally full time in the placement supported with a visit from a lifetime tutor.</p>
