      <p>We will help you with this by providing you with an exit interview, as well as a letter of reference and a certificate of completion.</p>
      <h3 class="heading-medium">Reality check</h3>
      <p>The opportunity will give you some experience in the workplace, and training to support your job search and applications.</p>
