        <p>This will be a 12 week traineeship where you will gain quality work experience in Fitness Instructing.
          The Traineeship program will also include off the job training in English, Maths and job search activity.
          Your first week will consist of guided learning with one of our tutors (Monday –Friday) weeks 2-7 will consist of you attending the placement work place 3 days a week full time and an additional 2 days a week will be back in the classroom with the tutor, weeks 8-12 will the totally full time in the placement supported with a visit from a lifetime tutor.</p>
          <p>Apprenticeships are a fantastic way to gain qualifications and relevant skills whilst earning money. </p>
          <p>Lifetime are different, we really care about you and your development and our visits to your workplace throughout your Apprenticeship are designed to make sure you’re getting everything you need to qualify with success.  You will also have access to a range of learner materials and a team of friendly advisors who you can call five days a week to ask any questions about your studies as you’re working through them.</p>
